comments.en: This Ontology helps to define wood damages in the field of construction. Experts in wood damages can use this ontology for writing reports. It is a sub-ontology to the "Damage Topology Ontology" and is defined as an "Classified damage". It defines damage types, connected causes, repair methods and investigation procedures. All these categories are part of the Report.
